timings.p: This is the set of grammar / test-case pairs for the timing data of 12 April 2022, made by matching records in the grammar-test and test-case timing data of that date.
The XQuery was ../lib/stratify-single-test-report.xq, run on the test report from 30 July 2022 for ixml-all.
Attributes: n for name (grammar/test-case), t = time in ms, gt = mean parse time for grammar (rounded to the ms), ct = mean parse time for test case (rounded). In all cases t = gt + ct.
